Package ca.openosp.openo.managers

Class DemographicManagerImpl

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.managers.DemographicManagerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
DemographicManager
@Service public class DemographicManagerImpl extends Object implements DemographicManager
Will provide access to demographic data, as well as closely related data such as extensions (DemographicExt), merge data, archive data, etc.

Future Use: Add privacy, sec, and consent profiles
